text: Natalya Akilova (born ) is a Kazakhstani female volleyball player. She is a member of the Kazakhstan women's national volleyball team and played for Zhetyssu in 2011. She was part of the Kazakhstani national team at the 2011 FIVB World Grand Prix in Italy. 2014 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2017 FIVB World Grand Prix, and 2018 Asian Games. == Clubs == * Zhetyssu (2011) == References == == External links == * FIVB profile * Natalya Akilova Pictures in Zimbio Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Kazakhstani women's volleyball players Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Volleyball players at the 2014 Asian Games Category:Volleyball players at the 2018 Asian Games
